products.title: Zambezi Pure White Real Wood
products.description: Their premium zambezi pure white real wood blind features a light white painted wood slat, great for freshening up your home. From soft stained brown shades, painted creamy neutrals to textured fine grains, this real wood range creates a natural chic finish to your windows. This white real wood blind would look at home in a rustic setting, or as a finishing touch to a neutral-toned room. At swift direct blinds, we take quality seriously.

At swift direct blinds quality is important to us, which is why your new perfect fit blind is hand-made with quality materials, in their yorkshire workshop by their team of experts, and delivered direct to your door.
